data 0,""
data 0,"- editing program and sharing them on the official website: https://ret.ro.it"
data 0,""
data 6,"It's better to login before sharing from the app."
data 0,""
data 0,"- the 'gfx' program can edit characters, palette and background, perfect on iPad and iPhone."
data 0,""
